**Capital Raising Announcement**  
- **Type:** Placement (two-tranche)  
- **Total Raised:** AUD 6.0 million (before costs)  
- **Issue Price:** AUD 0.065/share (15.8% discount to 20-day VWAP)  
- **Tranche 1 (ASX 7.1/7.1A):** 51.3 million shares, settling 11 July 2025  
- **Tranche 2 (Subject to EGM):** 41.0 million shares to major shareholder Longreach (51.1% pro-forma stake)  
- **Use of Funds:** Accelerate Kuda Tasi & Jahal project to FID (studies, FPSO due diligence, approvals)  
- **Post-Offer Metrics:** Market cap AUD 24.5M; enterprise value AUD 13.7M  
- **Post-Placement Shares Outstanding:** 376 million  

*Omitted: Broker names, EGM timing (not specified), forward-looking disclaimers.*
